  stepLabel: ENGINE BASE
  narrationText: "This is the engine block \u2014 the structural skeleton of the
    entire system.\n\nIt holds every moving part in precise alignment. Without this
    rigid frame, nothing could function under the forces of combustion.\n\nRight
    now it's hiding everything inside\u2026 so let's make it transparent \u2014 and
    reveal what's happening within."
